{"tid":537844,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本大雪記者奔車站直播！冒出搶鏡哥「鏡頭到哪都拍到你」","createTime":"2018-01-23T05:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T06:25:57.000Z","uid":9573,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb929fa27235dcf76413d3ac36e17f9b102f29f","tid":537844,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T05:24:10.000Z","msg":"日本各地22日狂下大雪，截至目前為止東京已經累積超過20公分的積雪量，在尖峰下班時段，電車紛紛延遲行駛，造成車站人擠人混亂場面！有電視台記者趕到新宿車站直播實況，結果有觀眾眼尖發現，無論鏡頭轉到哪裡都會拍到一個毛帽哥！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3069/d3069331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3069%2Fd3069331.jpg&h=6e22c660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本大雪記者戶外直播，冒出搶鏡哥。<br />\n<br />\n男子戴毛帽、黑框眼鏡，見到記者站在鏡頭前報新聞，原本在移動中的腳步瞬間停住，直盯著鏡頭露出笑容，緊接著鏡頭特寫大雪街頭，他的毛帽依然在鏡頭中。他接下來開始追著鏡頭跑，畫面正在拍驗票口，就趕來站在驗票口前，甚至和鏡頭的方向同步移動，搶鏡到最後一秒，原來他是網路有名的「搶鏡哥」，過去也曾出現在新聞畫面中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3069/d3069332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3069%2Fd3069332.jpg&h=e0adc183&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲鏡頭特寫街道，搶鏡哥毛帽還是入鏡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3069/d3069333.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3069%2Fd3069333.jpg&h=2c07c11d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲鏡頭轉過來拍車站，搶鏡哥也趕來了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3069/d3069334.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3069%2Fd3069334.jpg&h=26c2c804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲鏡頭緩慢移動，搶鏡哥也慢慢走。<br />\n<br />\n網友用手機翻拍新聞畫面，吐槽「看了這個，我笑到噴咖啡啦」，同時翻攝畫面上傳到推特，飆了124萬人觀看。搶鏡哥畫面造成熱烈討論，不少人都很關心狗年的運勢會如何，香港著名命理學家蘇民峰詳細講解生肖運勢，有人認為妨礙拍攝，更有不少人狂笑「看到嚇了一跳」、「我都噴茶了」、「鏡頭一度想逃到中間放棄了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3069/e3069330.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3069%2Fe3069330.jpg&h=1b731d16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲網友翻拍電視畫面，「我笑到噴咖啡」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/aroundthesekai/status/955338973483745280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faroundthesekai%2Fstatus%2F955338973483745280&d=0eq4qu%2FtDuichQRPO94KhZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=07182008\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faroundthesekai%2Fstatus%2F955338973483745280&h=87c5143d\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/aroundthesekai/status/955338973483745280</a>"},{"pid":"9dc7a2b1f3c025fbbde2d1b92bb7505be08e8837","tid":537844,"uid":166675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T05:40:57.000Z","msg":"最後張相露出勝利笑容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f404705d2ccea1eca9770683eb1e0e214f15de","tid":537844,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"attention seeker,同呢度某D人一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2208fe74a5d0f9f738f3be1f89e0be40d5d0d934","tid":537844,"uid":8795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:36:36.000Z","msg":"個樣好似sanma節目入面d東大生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d1d4c040d14388c25cbe4bde2d9f30e2d54dee","tid":537844,"uid":54486,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:38:25.000Z","msg":"不少人都很關心狗年的運勢會如何，香港著名命理學家蘇民峰詳細講解生肖運勢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f44fcd3bbfdd64299da78b2c18502317b25cb7","tid":537844,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:42:01.000Z","msg":"蓋青"},{"pid":"9d56329b627bd244c72eede40deef712c7e5cd49","tid":537844,"uid":2950,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f3d1